[32m+[m[32m## Features[m
 [m
[31m-* **Plan Selection**: Choose from a predefined list of engineering plans using a dropdown menu.[m
[31m-* **Dynamic Sections**: Add custom sections to your checklist for a selected plan.[m
[31m-* **Interactive Items**: Within each section, you can add, edit, and delete checklist items.[m
[31m-* **Pre-populated Data**: The app comes with two sample plans, "cofraj" and "armare," which are populated with default checklist data from `src/utilitary.js`.[m
